data.text:
Medical Scientist

Westmead.

Orig­i­nal­ly from Perth, West­ern Aus­tralia and grad­u­ate from the Uni­ver­si­ty of West­ern Aus­tralia. Masood com­plet­ed his Mas­ters of Clin­i­cal Pathol­o­gy in 2021 and has been work­ing in var­i­ous lab­o­ra­to­ries since. Cur­rent­ly Masood is the Research Coor­di­na­tor for Anatom­i­cal Pathol­o­gy. In this role he is respon­si­ble for the day to day coor­di­na­tion of research projects that require Anatom­i­cal pathol­o­gy services.
